<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/zh-cn/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/zh-cn/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><updated>2026-04-12T06:09:37+00:00</updated><id>https://jiaye-wu.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><entry><title type="html">[受邀讲座] 新型时域泰伯效应及其片上集成</title><link href="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/zh-cn/blog/2026/invited-THU/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="[受邀讲座] 新型时域泰伯效应及其片上集成"/><published>2026-04-10T10:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-04-10T10:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2026/invited-THU</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2026/invited-THU/"><![CDATA[<p><strong>2026年4月10日</strong>，应<strong>OPTICA/IEEE光子学会/SPIE清华大学深圳国际研究生院学生分会</strong>邀请，于<strong>清华大学 清华国际深圳研究生院（SIGS）</strong>开展题为《新型时域泰伯效应及其片上集成》的讲座。<a class="citation" href="#Wu2022a">(Wu et al., 2022; Wu et al., 2022; Wu et al., 2023)</a></p> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-4 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-01-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-01-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-01-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-01.png" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <div class="col-8 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-03-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-03-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-03-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-03.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-6 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-02-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-02-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-02-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-02.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <div class="col-6 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-04-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-04-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-04-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/post_contents/Talk-THU-04.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="talks"/><category term="research blog"/><category term="integrated photonics"/><category term="Talbot effect"/><category term="invited talk"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[时域泰伯效应系列受邀讲座]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">[受邀研讨会] Epsilon-Near-Zero Photonics: Crossroad of Multidisciplinary Research</title><link href="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/zh-cn/blog/2026/invited-THU-SIGS-iDI/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="[受邀研讨会] Epsilon-Near-Zero Photonics: Crossroad of Multidisciplinary Research"/><published>2026-04-09T10:30:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-04-09T10:30:00+00:00</updated><id>https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2026/invited-THU-SIGS-iDI</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2026/invited-THU-SIGS-iDI/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="news"/><category term="talks"/><category term="epsilon-near-zero"/><category term="plasmonics"/><category term="nonlinear optics"/><category term="integrated photonics"/><category term="nanophotonics"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[受邀于清华大学深圳国际研究生院数据与信息研究院作研讨会学术报告]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">[学术会议报告] ACP: Real-Time Observation of Ultrafast Thermo-Optic Nonlinearity in Time-Varying Effective Epsilon-Near-Zero Media</title><link href="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/zh-cn/blog/2025/conf-ACP/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="[学术会议报告] ACP: Real-Time Observation of Ultrafast Thermo-Optic Nonlinearity in Time-Varying Effective Epsilon-Near-Zero Media"/><published>2025-11-08T15:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-11-08T15:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2025/conf-ACP</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://jiaye-wu.github.io/blog/2025/conf-ACP/"><![CDATA[<p>今日在中国江苏省苏州市举办的<a href="https://acpconf.com/">Asian Communications and Photonics Conference (ACP) 2025</a>会议上作题为 <em>Real-Time Observation of Ultrafast Thermo-Optic Nonlinearity in Time-Varying Effective Epsilon-Near-Zero Media</em> 的学术报告。<a class="citation" href="#Wu2025ACP">(Wu*† et al., 2025)</a></p> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-7 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/post_contents/Conf-ACP-2025-01-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/post_contents/Conf-ACP-2025-01-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/post_contents/Conf-ACP-2025-01-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/post_contents/Conf-ACP-2025-01.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <div class="col-5 mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="res